{"name":"Ophelia Berendsen","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"","alignment":"","hitDice":"14","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (natural armor)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":true,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"91 (14d6 + 28)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"10","dexPoints":"16","conPoints":"13","intPoints":"16","wisPoints":"14","chaPoints":"20","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"10","customCr":"12 (8,400 XP)","customProf":4,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The archmage can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The archmage regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the archmage can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the archmage can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The archmage can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the archmage's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the archmage's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the archmage dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON] is an 14th-level spellcaster. Her spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC [CHA SAVE], [CHA ATK] to hit with spell attacks). [MON] has the following sorcerer spells known:\n\n> * Cantrips (at will): _ray of frost, dancing lights, mage hand, prestidigitation, shocking grasp, shape water_\n> * 1st level (4 slots): _charm person, shield, ice knife_\n> * 2nd level (3 slots): _detect thoughts, misty step_\n> * 3rd level (3 slots): _counterspell, slow_\n> * 4th level (3 slots): _greater invisibility, dimension door,_\n> * 5th level (2 slots): _summon **Cahuatelle**, dominate person,_\n> * 6th level (1 slot): _Otiluke's freezing sphere_\n> * 7th level (1 slot): _etherealness_"},{"name":"Metamagic (14/day)","desc":"[MON] has access to the following metamagic options:\n- Heightened Spell\n- Twinned Spell\n- Subtle Spell"},{"name":"Ice affinity","desc":"[MON] adds her proficiency bonus to damage rolls which do cold damage."},{"name":"Shared Resistances","desc":"While **Cahuatelle** is summoned, [MON] has shared resistance to one of his damage types. Additionally, she gains [2d4] temporary hit points every time **Cahuatelle** takes damage as she's surrounded in a barrier of blue and yellow sparks."},{"name":"Masked Ablate","desc":"[MON] is bound to a **Masked Ablate** via an amulet she keeps hidden. [MON] can telepathically call the **Ablate** to travel to it. If the **Ablate** is within 60 feet of [MON], half of any damage she takes (rounded up) is transferred to the **Ablate**."},{"name":"Stoic's Ring","desc":"[MON] has advantage on Wisdom saving throws"}],"actions":[{"name":"Claw","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft, one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1d4] piercing damage."},{"name":"Stoic's Ring","desc":"[MON] ends one frightened or charmed condition."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Heels of Hasty Retreat (1/Day)","desc":"[MON] clicks her heels together. Every creature within 20 ft must make a DC 15 strength saving throw or be pushed 15 feed back. [MON] may then immediately use her reaction to cast a spell targeting only herself."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Counterspell","desc":"[MON] casts _counterspell_."},{"name":"Shield","desc":"[MON] casts _shield_."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"int","order":3},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int"},{"name":"deception","stat":"cha","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"history","stat":"int"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"cold","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"specialdamage":[{"name":"shared: Cahuatelle","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Aire","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Draconic","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true},{"name":"Halfling","speaks":true},{"name":"Thieves' Cant","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Ophelia","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}